title: OnePlus 9RT, OnePlus 8 / 8 Pro and OnePlus Nord pick up new OxygenOS updates
content:

While the new software isn’t coming anytime soon, the company is keeping its smartphone portfolio up to date with the latest security patches and software improvements.
